OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPatchy cloud
OL,6,Falong with clear spells expected
OL,7,Fovernight. Generally mild initially
OL,8,Fbut becoming chilly later in the
OL,9,Fnight, with a patchy frost likely to
OL,10,Fdevelop towards dawn. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FAfter a chilly start, Tuesday
OL,13,Fwill be dry with plenty of sunny
OL,14,Fspells and light winds. Becoming
OL,15,Fchilly again overnight, with a patchy
OL,16,Ffrost expected.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
