OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FPatchy
OL,6,Fcloud and sunny spells expected
OL,7,FWednesday. Fog and low cloud
OL,8,Fdeveloping Wednesday night, slowly
OL,9,Fclearing through Thursday, before a
OL,10,Fband of rain moves east later. Sunny
OL,11,Fspells expected Friday.
